<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.3.11">
<l>uyvu pāya maṟṟiṉmai tēṟik kaṇṇa ṉoṇkaḻalkaḷmēl</l>
<l>ceyya tāma raippaḻaṉat teṉṉaṉ kurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>poyyil pāṭa lāyirattu ḷīvaiyum pattum vallārkaḷ</l>
<l>vaiya maṉṉi vīṟṟiruntu viṇṇu māḷvar maṇṇūṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten among the thousand in falseless song</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr of the Southern king with red lotus tanks</l>
<l>on the bright ankletted [feet] of Kṛṣṇa, being clear about the absence of any other means of salvation,</l>
<l>will remain in the world in eminent position [and] will rule heaven too on earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
